\ examples/01-void.6th
\ Canonical ladder, rung 1 — the void.
\
\ Before any distinction is drawn the substrate exists as a
\ possibility, not a fact.  Zero tokens, zero pointers, zero
\ structure.  This is the empty starting position from which every
\ subsequent demonstration grows.

use prelude
use debug

NODES 0 assert-eq
EDGES 0 assert-eq

cr
"=== Rung 1 — the void ===" . cr
"NODES = 0   EDGES = 0   nothing distinguished yet" . cr

REPORT
